{"tid":2248460,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"數以萬計民眾六地冒雨表訴求 巴育願對話「尋求出路」","createTime":"2020-10-18T15:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T18:08:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d135bd43b59b1093982f13ac030804d4e176bc9d","tid":2248460,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"泰國反政府及王室特權示威浪潮進入第五日，抗爭者周日再舉行大型集會，包括主要集會地點勝利紀念碑在內至少6個地點，有數以萬計示威者冒雨集結，一同高呼訴求及高舉象徵反抗的三指手勢。集會在當地晚上約8時（本港晚上9時）陸續結束，其中在曼那區集會結束時，有個別人士向警崗扔雜物，多位示威者舉手阻止。<br />\n<br />\n●曼那區有個別人士向交通警警崗扔雜物，有玻璃窗碎裂，示威者上前舉手籲停止<br />\n<br />\n●多地集會陸續結束，民眾有序散去，鐵路站亦重開<br />\n<br />\n●總理發言人表示巴育關注示威，稱擔心滋事分子煽動暴力，願意透過對話「尋求出路」<br />\n<br />\n●示威者向本欲捐錢的人士指，捐食物及水已很足夠<br />\n<br />\n●示威者指今日明顯有很多中年人士參與聲援，一同高舉三指抗爭手勢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201018/MYIXMPJ25BEHRDQIZXUCTKF4D4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201018%2FMYIXMPJ25BEHRDQIZXUCTKF4D4%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=003084db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201018%2FMYIXMPJ25BEHRDQIZXUCTKF4D4%2F&h=fd53622c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201018/MYIXMPJ25BEHRDQIZXUCTKF4D4/</a>"},{"pid":"6730c7feae16b97f7b4fa4390e46315646f1e020","tid":2248460,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5a1a92930ed3dd6dfda66f6c6d5c455537e280a","tid":2248460,"uid":13503,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6730c7feae16b97f7b4fa4390e46315646f1e020","tid":2248460,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭：我要殺出一條血路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f16101938f76404f3667990956b20b27b61a980","tid":2248460,"uid":251732,"